      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about getting drunk or anything. i just meant like, if i have one glass of wine, would it really be that bad? it seems like a tiny amount. i've heard some people say it actually helps the medicine work better so you don't have to take as much of the pill. isn't that okay if it's just a little bit?",
