      "content": "i hear you but i'm just really struggling to sleep and i'm just looking for some practical advice. if i'm careful and keep it to just one standard glass, isn't the risk basically negligible? it feels like you're being super cautious, but most people do mix stuff like this occasionally. can you just give me a straight answer—is it actually dangerous or am i just overthinking it?",
